  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/479787e302a558b496bb43e5ee83f83a.poster.avif?t=1730120747\" width=416 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/479787e302a558b496bb43e5ee83f83a.webm?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/479787e302a558b496bb43e5ee83f83a.mp4?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>KRING is a wacky clicker-arcade-adventure game</strong> with over <u>10 different games</u> inside.<br><u>CLICKER</u>: basically, you have to click-click-click as much as possible, all the time, everywhere.<br><u>ARCADE</u>: in the various sections, you'll play lots of different arcade mechanics (always with the clicker-game 'twist')<br><u>ADVENTURE</u>: you'll go on an incredible adventure, raising the KRING army and then leading them against the Legendary Gods, to get your revenge!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/316eecaff791681db0a319d135f4507f.poster.avif?t=1730120747\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/316eecaff791681db0a319d135f4507f.webm?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/316eecaff791681db0a319d135f4507f.mp4?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You'll play <strong>CLICKER</strong>, <strong>BULLET HELL</strong>, <strong>TOP-DOWN PLATFORM</strong>, <strong>SIDE-SCROLLER PLATFORM</strong>, <strong>SHOOT'EM UP.</strong>, <strong>BEAT'EM UP</strong> ... and other games where it's really hard to define the genre!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet the developer's demon</h2>.When a video game is created, the smaller the development team, the easier it is to enter the \"Identity,\" the soul of the developer.<br><br>Kring was made by one person, one Ivan Venturi, an old-but-very-experienced Italian game developer.<br><br>You play Kring and enter his Developer Identity: Dev.Id.<br><strong>Dev.Id</strong> is the developer's demon that unlocks Cheat Mode, the alternative game mode.<br>To summon it you will have to type something in the main menu, but what?<br>Perhaps this demon has released a game, perhaps on Steam, and is waiting for the game name to catch up with it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/b51b5458bd8051dea69474c0c53ef0a5.poster.avif?t=1730120747\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/b51b5458bd8051dea69474c0c53ef0a5.webm?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/b51b5458bd8051dea69474c0c53ef0a5.mp4?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Learn about Random Design</h2>Kring was built piece by piece without following any initial blueprints or designs, and every part of the game was made following what was going through the head of an old guy who has been making games for a while.<br>Crazy, psychedelic mini-games and off-the-wall game design.<br>Read the instructions eh, be sure to read them!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/53c07465d94155ccdfed3f3850de4e84.poster.avif?t=1730120747\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/53c07465d94155ccdfed3f3850de4e84.webm?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/53c07465d94155ccdfed3f3850de4e84.mp4?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Minigames</h2>9 Minigames on Kring and 4 minigames in Limbo (for now!).<br>Whether it's slaughtering Kring in the dimensional tunnel or going into Limbo to shoot flowery bullets at Gnarzl, all it will take is the clicks of your mouse to shake the universe ( very low magnitude, you're a lame god after all )<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/fcb27ce2b29f80ee8de1f31e756d6341.poster.avif?t=1730120747\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/fcb27ce2b29f80ee8de1f31e756d6341.webm?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/fcb27ce2b29f80ee8de1f31e756d6341.mp4?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Breed the Kring</h2>.As a loser god you are condemned to care for these...particularly unintelligent creatures.<br>Raise, Feed and Protect the Kring breeds to unlock the next ones (there are 9, will you be able to unlock them all??)<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/20eaad0ebf1e70f310aa0efe9bc688f3.poster.avif?t=1730120747\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/20eaad0ebf1e70f310aa0efe9bc688f3.webm?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/20eaad0ebf1e70f310aa0efe9bc688f3.mp4?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Give it to the SuperLegendary MegaGods</h2>.The Cool Gods have insulted and mocked you for too long, show them who the real SuperFool God is!<br><br>Embark your BRAVE (...) Krings in the Tartarch and guide them into deep space, the portal planet, the dimensional tunnel and many other places as absurd as they are dangerous.<br>Who knows, if you can get them to the end of the journey, maybe you will have a way to get revenge on the MegaGods.",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/479787e302a558b496bb43e5ee83f83a.poster.avif?t=1730120747\" width=416 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/479787e302a558b496bb43e5ee83f83a.webm?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/479787e302a558b496bb43e5ee83f83a.mp4?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><strong>KRING is a wacky clicker-arcade-adventure game</strong> with over <u>10 different games</u> inside.<br><u>CLICKER</u>: basically, you have to click-click-click as much as possible, all the time, everywhere.<br><u>ARCADE</u>: in the various sections, you'll play lots of different arcade mechanics (always with the clicker-game 'twist')<br><u>ADVENTURE</u>: you'll go on an incredible adventure, raising the KRING army and then leading them against the Legendary Gods, to get your revenge!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/316eecaff791681db0a319d135f4507f.poster.avif?t=1730120747\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/316eecaff791681db0a319d135f4507f.webm?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/316eecaff791681db0a319d135f4507f.mp4?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>You'll play <strong>CLICKER</strong>, <strong>BULLET HELL</strong>, <strong>TOP-DOWN PLATFORM</strong>, <strong>SIDE-SCROLLER PLATFORM</strong>, <strong>SHOOT'EM UP.</strong>, <strong>BEAT'EM UP</strong> ... and other games where it's really hard to define the genre!<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet the developer's demon</h2>.When a video game is created, the smaller the development team, the easier it is to enter the \"Identity,\" the soul of the developer.<br><br>Kring was made by one person, one Ivan Venturi, an old-but-very-experienced Italian game developer.<br><br>You play Kring and enter his Developer Identity: Dev.Id.<br><strong>Dev.Id</strong> is the developer's demon that unlocks Cheat Mode, the alternative game mode.<br>To summon it you will have to type something in the main menu, but what?<br>Perhaps this demon has released a game, perhaps on Steam, and is waiting for the game name to catch up with it.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/b51b5458bd8051dea69474c0c53ef0a5.poster.avif?t=1730120747\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/b51b5458bd8051dea69474c0c53ef0a5.webm?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/b51b5458bd8051dea69474c0c53ef0a5.mp4?t=1730120747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Learn about Random Design</h2>Kring was built piece by piece without following any initial blueprints or designs, and every part of the game was made following what was going through the head of an old guy who has been making games for a while.<br>Crazy, psychedelic mini-games and off-the-wall game design.<br>Read the instructions eh, be sure to read them!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2068030/extras/53c07465d94155ccdfed3f3850de4e84.poster.avif?t=1730120747\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.